  "title": "Ultra-Hold Acrylic Diamond Liquid Adhesive",
  "body_html": "<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_wc_description et_pb_wc_description_0 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_left\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">The longer-lasting acrylic adhesive on the market. It provides a solid bond for up to 3 weeks, and is water and sweat-resistant, making it the perfect solution for high-performance athletes. It can also be combined with water-based adhesives to get all the benefits of both products: the best hold and easy clean-up.</p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Advantages</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Transparent.</li>\n<li>Extra resistant to water and sweat.</li>\n<li>Hold up to three weeks.</li>\n<li>Easy to clean.</li>\n<li>Specific formulation for hair bonding: hair prosthesis, wigs, and extensions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Format</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<p>Bottle with a brush for easy application.</p>\n<p>Quantity: 15 ml.</p>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Recommendations for use</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Apply to the scalp and not to the hair system.</li>\n<li>Apply to the outer edge of the desired area to be bonded.\u00a0Then spread the product evenly, applying the right amount to create a thin layer.</li>\n<li>Applying at least 2 or 3 layers is highly recommended, allowing the glue to dry 2-3 minutes between each coat application.</li>\n<li>Allow the glue to dry for a few minutes before attaching your capillary system.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle et_pb_module et_pb_accordion_item et_pb_accordion_item_3 et_clickable et_pb_toggle_open\">\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Product safety data sheet</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://luxhair.es/en/Product/luxhair-diamond-liquid-adhesive#:~:text=safety%20data%20sheet-,Link,-Related%20products\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Link</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_wc_add_to_cart et_pb_wc_add_to_cart_0 et_pb_fields_label_position_default et_pb_bg_layout_  et_pb_text_align_left\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><form enctype=\"multipart/form-data\" method=\"post\" action=\"https://luxhair.es/en/Product/luxhair-diamond-liquid-adhesive\" class=\"cart\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"quantity\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<ul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></ul>\n\u00a0</div>\n</form></div>\n</div>",
